  <summary date="2019-08-20T13:43:57Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Tribal School Federal Insurance Parity Act

This bill amends the Indian Health Care Improvement Act to allow tribes or tribal organizations that receive grants under the Tribally Controlled Schools Act of 1988 to participate in the Federal Employee Health Benefits program.</summary>
